text: Kandry-Tyumekeyevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Nikolayevsky Selsoviet, Tuymazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 135 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 35 km from Tuymazy, 8 km from Nikolayevka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tuymazinsky District
title: Kandry-Tyumekeyevo
